data.description: You'll love to come home to this 4+ ACRE, PRIVATE RETREAT with in-ground HEATED, SALTWATER POOL! VA assumable loan is option for fellow veterans using VA loan!  Interest rate is 2.3% Fabulous Huntingtown location--of excellent blue-ribbon schools, and so close to DC & Joint Base Andrews. Perfect property  if you like to entertain,  or enjoy the great outdoors! Go 4-wheeling with the family in the secluded woods then relax in the pool that has a 10' deep end with diving board, or sip drinks in the screened-in gazebo or pool bar.   Property has two creeks/streams that run that run through the back part of the land. This home has endless upgrades and improvements, including a new pool heater and a new custom pool cover in 2023.  Has an updated kitchen with Scandinavian-style cabinets, stainless steel appliances including Sub Zero Refrigerator, electric cook top, double ovens, and a new built-in microwave. Has recessed lighting in the kitchen as well as upgraded Corian countertops and a tiled backsplash.  The walk-out basement was finished in 2022 ($80k) with  possible in-law apartment, including the 5th bedroom and full bath.  With the added bedroom and bath, a new upgraded septic system was installed in 2022 ($60k), including two tanks and new drain fields, an alarm system and lifetime warranty.  Has a Other upgrades and improvements sellers have done include new garage doors in 2023,  gravel RV/camper parking pad 2020, outside motion lights installed 2021, a new water softer system 2022, new well pump 2019, new custom cabinets in dining room 2021 ($5k), new ceiling fans installed in all rooms 2021.  Roof is only five years old. Home has been freshly painted throughout and has new carpet too! It's like buying a new home with the amount of improvements and thorough maintenance these sellers have done, including having all ducts, vents and the chimney cleaned in 2022.  Home is extremely energy efficient, as it's heated and cooled by a GEOTHERMAL system with electronic air filtration that is connected to a hot water system!  No HOA here-- so no extra fees, and the freedom to truly enjoy this property how you wish!
